        "description": "<p><a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/upwork\">Upwork</a> ($UPWK) is the world’s work marketplace. We serve everyone from one-person startups to large, Fortune 100 enterprises with a powerful, trust-driven platform that enables companies and talent to work together in new ways that unlock their potential.</p><p>Last year, more than $3.8 billion of work was done through <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/upwork\">Upwork</a> by skilled professionals who are gaining more control by finding work they are passionate about and innovating their careers.</p><p>This is an engagement through <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/upwork\">Upwork</a>’s Hybrid Workforce Solutions (HWS) Team. Our Hybrid Workforce Solutions Team is a global group of professionals that support <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/upwork\">Upwork</a>’s business. Our HWS team members are located all over the world.</p><hr><h3><strong>Work/Project Scope:</strong></h3><ul>\n<li>Delivering creative work of exceptional standard, reflecting <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/upwork\">Upwork</a>'s renowned reputation. Presenting a portfolio showcasing outstanding motion graphics work and a distinct creative vision.</li>\n<li>Working on assigned projects following briefs and under the guidance of an Art Director, while adhering to deadlines and project scope.</li>\n<li>Creating high-quality 2D/3D motion graphics for diverse projects, such as paid ads, videos, and organic social channels.</li>\n<li>Adapting animations to suit the technical constraints of different platforms and devices.</li>\n<li>Understanding project goals, daily tasks, and deadlines, while maintaining an ability to work independently and collaboratively within a team.</li>\n<li>Collaborating closely with Senior Designers, Art Directors, Creative Directors, and Producers to ensure timely delivery of work that aligns with the creative and technical requirements of the brief.</li>\n<li>Assisting in the development of responses to creative motion briefs.</li>\n<li>Actively participating in departmental meetings, creative activities, and cross-functional partnerships.</li>\n<li>Responding to feedback from Art Directors, producers, and cross-functional partners, making necessary adjustments to creative work, and offering valuable insights and ideas to progress projects.</li>\n<li>Receiving feedback from the broader team and cross-functional partners to ensure only the highest quality work is produced.</li>\n<li>Supporting and enforcing <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/upwork\">Upwork</a>'s motion workflow and processes, offering guidance and education to team members as needed.</li>\n<li>Staying up-to-date with the latest trends and innovations in motion graphics and applying them to <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/upwork\">Upwork</a>'s projects.</li>\n<li>Participating in regular check-ins with creative colleagues, Art Directors, Design Directors, Creative Directors, and Producers to monitor project progress.</li>\n</ul><h3>Must Haves (Required Skills):</h3><ul>\n<li>Detail-oriented with a thinker/maker mindset.</li>\n<li>Experience in working on conceptual campaigns of both large and small scales.</li>\n<li>Proven ability to collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams.</li>\n<li>Self-driven, organized, detail-oriented, and skilled in multitasking.</li>\n<li>Strong written communication skills.</li>\n<li>A keen sense of timing and direction.</li>\n<li>Excellent interpersonal and team-working skills.</li>\n<li>Proficient knowledge of current trends and innovations in motion graphics.</li>\n</ul><hr><p><a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/upwork\">Upwork</a> is proudly committed to fostering a diverse and inclusive workforce. We never discriminate based on race, religion, color, national origin, gender (including pregnancy, childbirth, or related medical condition), sexual orientation, gender identity, gender expression, age, status as a protected veteran, status as an individual with a disability, or other applicable legally protected characteristics. </p><div class=\"content-conclusion\"><p>To learn more about how <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/upwork\">Upwork</a> processes and protects your personal information as part of the application process, please review our <a href=\"http://upwork.com/careers/job-applicant-privacy-notice\">Global Job Applicant Privacy Notice</a></p></div><p>Originally posted on <a href='https://himalayas.app'>Himalayas</a></p>",
