        "description": "<div class=\"content-intro\">\n<p><em>This is a 100% fully remote role. Work virtually from anywhere in the Continental U.S.</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.govaris.com/\"></a><a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/varis\">Varis</a> is a well-funded and fast-growing technology startup that focuses on digital commerce software-as-a-service and procurement and is owned by The ODP Corporation (NASDAQ: ODP). We are innovation driven, customer centric, and ready to transform eProcurement and business-to-business (B2B) Marketplaces. Our culture is focused on a bold vision, launching the simplest (yet still valuable) solutions to learn, then either failing or scaling fast as we iterate towards our product goals.</p>\n<p>Joining us now is a ground-floor opportunity to shape our limitless future. You will see and feel the direct impact of your work, be surrounded by passionate people, learn how to be an entrepreneur, and be at the center of a highly dynamic business model with tremendous individual and collective potential.</p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong><br><strong>Your Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Responsible for <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/varis\">Varis</a> customer acquisition from prospect to close.</li>\n<li>Develop and execute a prospecting strategy based on emails, calls, and conference attendance to find new prospects and convert existing leads.</li>\n<li>Develop sales from business partnerships.</li>\n<li>Conduct comprehensive discovery calls with decision makers to assess alignment with <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/varis\">Varis</a> value proposition.</li>\n<li>Demonstrate a clear understanding of the SaaS sales process, Private Sector procurement needs, ideal customer profile, and <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/varis\">Varis</a> value proposition.</li>\n<li>Apply challenge selling to demonstrate tailored solutions based on customer needs.</li>\n<li>Present tailored demonstration of <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/varis\">Varis</a> solution.</li>\n<li>Consistently land mid-sized Private Sector customers based on sales targets.</li>\n<li>Serve as a highly motivated professional who does what is right for the customer.</li>\n<li>Remain ahead of the curve with respect to the latest sales trends, economic indicators, and newest technologies, including competitor research.</li>\n<li>Establish and maintain both technical and business credibility with customer leadership.</li>\n<li>Build strong internal, external, and cross-functional relationships</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Success Metrics</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Meet (or exceed) individual sales quotas/targets.</li>\n<li>Achieve (or exceed) team sales quotas/targets.</li>\n<li>Deliver successful new territory launches.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Who You Are</strong><br><strong>Cultural + Technical:</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Model our 5C Culture with expanded emphasis on:<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Customer:</strong> Relentlessly focus on serving our customers to ensure their success and deliver value.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Commitment:</strong> Set achievable but aggressive goals for the team and sacrifice personal gain in the pursuit.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Change:</strong> Partner with peers across the business and empower associates to find better/more efficient ways of working.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Caring:</strong> Provide effective, ongoing coaching that focuses on shared outcomes.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Creativity:</strong> Encourage the team to take calculated risks and explore new opportunities.</li>\n</ul>\n</li></ul>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Need</strong><br><strong>Education, Experience, Preferred Certifications/Designations:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bachelor’s Degree or equivalent experience.</li>\n<li>Full cycle sales experience with a strong track record of surpassing sales targets. Also, open to strong BDR experience.</li>\n<li>4 years or more of selling to mid-market organizations.</li>\n<li>Familiarity with SaaS technology/E-Commerce.</li>\n<li>Experience with Challenger or Consultative Sales methodologies</li>\n<li>Hunting and Closing skill set</li>\n<li>Ability to work with both short (30-90 days) and longer sales cycles.</li>\n<li>Ability to work in a dynamic, fast-paced environment while successfully managing multiple tasks and projects.</li>\n<li>Excellent communication skills and ability to effectively work, influence, problem solve, and engage with all levels of the organization.</li>\n<li>Proven track record in adapting to change.</li>\n<li>KPI and goal driven.</li>\n<li>Travel required: ~10% of time.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"content-pay-transparency\"><div class=\"pay-input\">\n<div class=\"description\">At <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/varis\">Varis</a>, pay scales are determined by role, level, location and alignment with market data. Individual pay is determined through interviews and an assessment of several factors that that are unique to each candidate, including but not limited to, job-related skills, relevant education and experience, certifications, abilities of the candidate and pay relative to other team members. <br><br>The figures in this range reflect the average annual base salary for the given role, while additional variable incentives based on performance may also be available. Recruiters can share more information about our bonus program, benefits and equity during the hiring process.</div>\n<div class=\"title\">Pay Range</div>\n<div class=\"pay-range\">$90,000$110,000 USD</div>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"content-conclusion\">\n<hr>\n<p><em>The above statements are intended to describe the general nature and level of work being performed by associates assigned to this classification and are not intended to be a complete list of all required responsibilities and skills. Other duties and special projects may be assigned per business needs. Job descriptions are subject to change at any time with or without notice.</em></p>\n<h3>Benefits and Perks</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>100% permanent remote work in the United States</li>\n<li>Medical / dental / vision, ADD, and Life Insurance</li>\n<li>Paid Time Offer (PTO) and company paid holidays</li>\n<li>Health Saving Account (HSA)</li>\n<li>Long Term Disability and Short-Term Disability</li>\n<li>401(k) matching program</li>\n<li>Discounted auto, home, and pet insurance</li>\n<li>Retirement savings plan rollovers</li>\n<li>Banking services</li>\n<li>Military leave</li>\n<li>Employee Assistance Program (EAP)</li>\n<li>Regular pay for funeral/memorial service observance</li>\n<li>Discounts on Office Depot/Microsoft/Apple products and services</li>\n<li>Opportunity for professional growth and career advancement</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/varis\">Varis</a> is wholly owned by The ODP Corporation, which is the legal employer of <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/varis\">Varis</a> associates.</em></p>\n<p><em>The ODP Corporation is an Equal Opportunity Employer. </em><em>We are committed to providing equal employment opportunities in all employment practices. All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, national origin, citizenship status, marital status, age, disability, protected veteran status, sexual orientation, or any other characteristic protected by law. We will consider for employment qualified applicants with arrest and conviction records in alignment with the City  County of San Francisco Fair Chance Ordinance.</em></p>\n<p><em>CCPA disclosure notice <a href=\"https://cdn-static.findly.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/655/2020/01/CCPA-Applicant-Privacy-Notice-Office-Depot-Inc..pdf\">here</a>.</em></p>\n</div>\n</div><p>Originally posted on <a href='https://himalayas.app'>Himalayas</a></p>",
