        "description": "<div>The Delivery Engineering team at <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/netflix\">Netflix</a> is building <a href=\"https://www.spinnaker.io/\" class=\"postings-link\">Spinnaker</a>, our Continuous Delivery platform, which facilitates <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/netflix\">Netflix</a> in delivering billions of hours of movies and TV shows per month.  The ability to rapidly and confidently deploy the code that directly affects the <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/netflix\">Netflix</a> experience is a huge competitive advantage. Whether it's an internal tool, a new recommendation algorithm, or changing the UI to showcase Squid Game, teams across <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/netflix\">Netflix</a> rely on Delivery Engineering's Continuous Delivery platform to make it happen.</div><div>We are looking for senior software engineers to join our Delivery Engineering team. We’re eager to talk to you if you’re passionate about building software that enables developers to use the cloud more effectively, enables developers to deploy code to production, and accelerates developer productivity.</div><h3>What you will do:</h3><ul>\n<li>Build, improve, and optimize the UI experience in <a href=\"https://www.spinnaker.io/\" class=\"postings-link\">Spinnaker</a>, <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/netflix\">Netflix</a>’s Continuous Delivery platform</li>\n<li>Partner with product management, product designers, backend engineers, and UI engineers to define and refine the user experience for our continuous delivery platform</li>\n<li>Collaborate with stakeholders to understand their needs and use cases for continuous delivery</li>\n</ul><h3>The skills we require:</h3><ul>\n<li>Great communication skills, both verbal and written</li>\n<li>Experience building web applications using JavaScript, HTML, CSS</li>\n<li>Passionate about user experience and have an eye for improving UIs</li>\n<li>Desire to work in a fast paced and dynamic environment</li>\n</ul><h3>The skills we prefer:</h3><ul>\n<li>Experience with <a href=\"http://React.js\" class=\"postings-link\">React.js</a>\n</li>\n<li>Passion for intuitive user interfaces</li>\n<li>Experience with AWS, GCP, or similar cloud computing environment</li>\n</ul><div>Our culture is unique, and we live by our <a href=\"https://jobs.netflix.com/culture\" class=\"postings-link\">values</a>, allowing you to do your best work and grow.</div><div>We are an equal opportunity employer and celebrate diversity, recognizing that diversity of thought and background builds stronger teams. We approach diversity and inclusion seriously and thoughtfully. We do not discriminate based on race, religion, color, national origin, gender, sexual orientation, age, marital status, veteran status, or disability status.</div><div>At <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/netflix\">Netflix</a>, we carefully consider a wide range of compensation factors to determine your personal top of market. We rely on market indicators to determine compensation and consider your specific job family, background, skills, and experience to get it right. These considerations can cause your compensation to vary and will also be dependent on your location. </div><div>The overall market range for roles in this area of <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/netflix\">Netflix</a> is typically $90,000 - $900,000</div><div>This market range is based on total compensation (vs. only base salary), which is in line with our compensation philosophy. <a href=\"https://himalayas.app/companies/netflix\">Netflix</a> is a unique culture and environment. Learn more <a href=\"https://jobs.netflix.com/culture\" class=\"postings-link\">here</a>.</div><p>Originally posted on <a href='https://himalayas.app'>Himalayas</a></p>",
